        <h3>Quest and Save Stability</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Quest progress persisted correctly across Save/Load.</li>
          <li>Objective state and completed quest state were preserved.</li>
          <li>No duplicate rewards or progression resets were observed.</li>
          <li>NPC state and world state remained stable after reloads.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="card">
        <h3>Performance and Boundaries</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Gameplay remained stable at around 60 FPS during normal play.</li>
          <li>Save operations were effectively instant.</li>
          <li>Load times remained under 2 seconds during testing.</li>
          <li>No out-of-bounds access, stuck locations, or terrain falls were found.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
